{"article_id":"LzKczw2qC78r6YUg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"The Senate Republican health care bill teetered on the edge of collapse Monday evening","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"after the Congressional Budget Office released a devastating report on its impact","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"and multiple Republicans announced","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"they would not vote to advance the legislation .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"The mood was tense and chaotic on Capitol Hill","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"moments","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"after the non-partisan agency predicted","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that the Republican proposal would result in 22 million more people becoming uninsured by 2026 years than under Obamacare .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Senate Republicans ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"many of whom are still undecided on whether to vote for the bill later this week ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"struggled to defend the legislation to mobs of reporters","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"who flocked to them for initial reactions .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"In a particularly ominous sign for Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"who has decided to move ahead with a vote later this week","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"despite widespread reservations among his colleagues ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"it was unclear whether he would even have the needed votes","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to clear an initial procedural hurdle .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Responding to the Republican opposition in the Senate to the current bill ,","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"a White House official conceded ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"`` We 're right on the threshold ''","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"of losing on health care .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"The official remarked","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"should the legislation collapse in the Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"the White House would simply move on to tax reform ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"noting","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"there is the potential for some bipartisan support for that effort .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"Kentucky Sen. Rand Paul ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"who opposes the GOP health care bill ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"told reporters","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"he would vote against the procedural step","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"-- known as a motion","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"to proceed --","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"if the legislation remained unchanged .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Maine Sen. Susan Collins , a moderate","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"who has been deeply critical of the health care bill ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"took the same position .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` I want to work w/ my GOP & Dem colleagues","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"to fix the flaws in ACA .","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"CBO analysis shows","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"Senate bill wo n't do it .","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"I will vote no on mtp , ''","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"Collins wrote on Twitter .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"( Earlier in the evening , Collins told reporters","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that the CBO score was `` obviously not positive . '' )","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"Senate Majority Whip John Cornyn had hinted earlier in the day","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that the Senate could move on the motion to proceed by Tuesday ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"but that came before the CBO analysis .","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Wisconsin GOP Sen. Ron Johnson , another holdout","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"who has publicly blistered the process","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"by which the Senate bill has moved through the upper chamber ,","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"said bluntly","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"that it would be a `` mistake '' to move forward with the motion","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"to proceed .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"`` If Leader McConnell says","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"failure is not an option ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"do n't set yourself up for failure would be my advice for the leader , ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Johnson told reporters .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Republican backers of the bill highlighted what they said","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"is CBO 's poor record of predictions .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"`` The CBO has consistently proven","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"it can not accurately predict how healthcare legislation will impact insurance coverage , ''","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"the White House said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"With the GOP health care process in jeopardy ,","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"the White House appeared to be ramping up its outreach to skeptical lawmakers .","depth":6},{"id":66,"text":"President Donald Trump himself spoke with several senators over the weekend ,","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"White House spokesman Sean Spicer said Monday .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"Collins told CNN","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that White House Chief of Staff Reince Priebus had reached out to her","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"to discuss the issue .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence will host four senators Tuesday night for dinner at the Naval Observatory :","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Sens . James Lankford , Mike Lee , Ben Sasse and Tom Cotton","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"( Lee has come out against the bill in its current form ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"while Lankford , Lee and Cotton are undecided ) .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"But it 's unclear just how big of a role Trump is playing in the ongoing Senate deliberations .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Some Senate Republicans are cautioning","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"that the President may not even back up senators","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"if public opinion on their health care bill flops in upcoming months .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"They are pointing to the fact","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"that Trump called the House health care bill `` mean '' to senators","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"a month after he hosted a celebration in the White House Rose Garden after the bill 's passage .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"`` Here 's what I would tell any senator :","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"If you 're counting on the President to have your back ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"you need to watch it , ''","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"GOP Sen. Lindsey Graham said .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"The Senate GOP health care bill explained","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"The Senate GOP health care bill explained","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"02:02","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"With public opposition mounting ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"GOP leaders may still make more changes to the original draft bill","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"to woo lawmakers","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"who are on the fence .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"But time is running out for those negotiations .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"South Dakota Sen. John Thune , a member of Senate leadership , said","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"something could be added to the bill","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"to assuage conservatives concerns","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"that the bill does n't repeal enough Obamacare regulations .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"But he also cautioned","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"that `` for the most part , the dimensions of the bill are starting to take shape . ''","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"`` I think","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"there probably is a way","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"you could address at least some of the issues","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"they 've raised , ''","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"Thune said .","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"as McConnell searches for 50 votes ,","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"he will be haunted by complicated political dynamics","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"that made passage of a health care bill so difficult in the House earlier this year :","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Giving concessions to lawmakers on one end of the political spectrum could turn off members of different ideological sway .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"This balancing act dogged House Speaker Paul Ryan in his quest","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"to pass an Obamacare repeal bill ,","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"even forcing him in March to yank a bill from the House floor .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"Ryan , for his part , declined to answer questions","depth":6},{"id":117,"text":"when asked about the CBO Monday afternoon .","depth":6},{"id":118,"text":"Democrats have been furious about Republican efforts","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"to gut Obamacare , former President Barack Obama 's landmark accomplishment .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"But Monday 's CBO report appeared to put some Democrats in a visibly good mood","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"as they watched their GOP colleagues squirm .","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"As Collins rode the escalator up to Senate votes","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"surrounded by reporters Monday afternoon ,","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"she happened to be walking next to Democratic Sen. Al Franken .","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"When a reporter asked Collins","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"whether she would like to see the legislation slow down ,","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"Franken chimed in :","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"`` I want to hear this . ''","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"Collins responded","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"that she was still reviewing the CBO report ,","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"but that `` it 's obviously not positive . ''","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"Franken , to laughter from reporters","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"listening in ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"quipped :","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"`` Very well done . ''","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":271,"left":0,"right":270,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":220,"right":269,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":220,"left":198,"right":219,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":198,"left":152,"right":197,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":152,"left":143,"right":151,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":139,"right":142,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":1,"right":138,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":2,"right":137,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":137,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":5,"right":141,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":6,"right":140,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":151,"left":146,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":144,"right":145,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":144,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":148,"right":149,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":13,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":161,"right":196,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":155,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":18,"right":154,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":154,"left":19,"right":153,"relation":"attribution","